040	MAT	001	013	Zerubbabel of Abiud, Abiud of Eliakim, Eliakim of Azor,
040	MAT	001	014	Azor of Zadok, Zadok of Achim, Achim of Eliud,
040	MAT	001	015	Eliud of Eleazar, Eleazar of Matthan, Matthan of Jacob,
040	MAT	001	016	Jacob of Joseph, the husband of Mary, who was the mother of Jesus, who is called ‘Christ’.
